request: Receive user request
clear: Is the request clear?
ask: Ask one focused question
update: Update request details
skill: Identify target skill
load: Load skill instructions
draft: Prepare D2 flow diagram
available: D2 CLI available?
render: Render Unicode flow diagram
return: Return diagram to user
setup: Show setup instructions
verify: Ask user to verify D2

request -> clear
clear -> skill: yes
clear -> ask: no
ask -> update
update -> skill
skill -> load
load -> draft
draft -> available
available -> render: yes
render -> return
available -> setup: no
setup -> verify
